data.title: A great find
data.text: Mikes place small. Six tables, fantastic all natural, home made food. This is our fourth time eating here . All food is made to order with local and organic natural food. The staff is very friendly and attentive.  Very clean . I have had corned beef hash, was excellent. Today I had eggs red potatoes and sausage. Yesterday I had the ham streak and eggs. This is one big slice of ham, perfectly cooked, we also had French toast big slices of bread , with a bowl of fruit. Today's meal for three was $27.00  if you want quality home made food at great price nice quiet place in Kenniwick find mikes place average cost 6.99 to $950
